 <p>For professionals and managers who operate internationally, the knowledge and expertise needed to work with people from other cultures and seek workable solutions to problems are just as important as technical skills. We offer you training and staff development programmes that are tailored to your needs.</p>

##PageID 3462
TEXT_content
 Evaluations examine activities at specific intervals to ascertain whether they produce results and are effective. They enable to learn from experience, place the management of measures on a firm foundation and account for actions. Since 2006, GIZ has had an accredited evaluation system that is aligned with international standards.

##PageID 3463
