 <p>Getting kids excited about a subject, motivating teachers, building bridges between schools, parents and communities – school competitions can be used in many different ways. They promote creativity and support learning processes and development. Working with schools has a very broad impact, which makes school competitions an interesting option for other sectors as well. Hold a school competition and get things moving!</p>

